== What triggers eczema

- some people notice specific triggers for their ecezma; others do not
- triggers can change over time as well

Triggers to trial avoiding:
- fabric softeners
- fragranced detergents, soaps, shampoos
- hot showers (if mirror is fogging, water is too hot!) heat dries out skin
- pat dry, don't scrub dry
avoid long fingernails, cut them short
avoid wool and tight clothing; cotton silk is preferred

