== What is 'Active Eczema'? or how do we know if I have a flare of eczema?

If your skin has any of: persistent itch, red, scaly, oozing, skin is more raised/rough
- if no, continue prevention - moisturizer daily, avoid triggers
- if yes, need to calm down that inflammation before it gets worse

